  - m_Id: 7163621376
    m_Localized: Survivor Intake Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7163621377
    m_Localized: A free intake drop for a cold district start. Expect one worker,
      one food source, and barely enough salvage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7511748608
    m_Localized: District Utility Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7511748609
    m_Localized: Broad early supplies for stabilizing the board. Good for Scrap,
      Rations, basic nodes, and first recipes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7809544192
    m_Localized: Kernel Research Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7813738496
    m_Localized: Encrypted leads, archive fragments, and volatile access pieces.
      Buy when the district can survive a bad draw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7926984704
    m_Localized: Hydroponics Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7926984705
    m_Localized: Food loops, nutrient beds, and docile production units. Builds long-term
      ration stability.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8103145472
    m_Localized: Recovery Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8107339776
    m_Localized: Prepared meals and recovery components for hungry crews. Turns survival
      pressure into margin.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8338026496
    m_Localized: Signal Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8338026497
    m_Localized: Archive hardware, relay parts, and blueprint-heavy draws. Use it
      to unlock smarter infrastructure.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8501604352
    m_Localized: Armory Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8501604353
    m_Localized: Fabrication stock, weapons, and hostile field tests. Good when defense
      becomes cheaper than fear.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8631627776
    m_Localized: Blackout Expedition Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8631627777
    m_Localized: Risk-heavy sector access with threats and area cards. Sends the
      board into the dark for better salvage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8660987904
    m_Localized: Infrastructure Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8660987905
    m_Localized: High-cost construction support for expanded district logistics.
      Heavy parts, generators, and storage lines.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8698736640
    m_Localized: Floodline Salvage Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8698736641
    m_Localized: A remote-sector starter cache from the drowned edge of the city.
      Coolant, black coral, and hard rubble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8715513856
    m_Localized: Emergency Survival Crate
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8715513857
    m_Localized: Cheap stabilization for failing runs. Basic salvage, coolant, and
      one reliable marker.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8740679680
    m_Localized: Blackout Yard
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8740679681
    m_Localized: An open work yard under dead billboards. Good salvage, poor cover.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8744873984
    m_Localized: Relay Graveyard
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8744873985
    m_Localized: A maze of fallen masts and live wire. Signals still move through
      it in bad shapes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8757456896
    m_Localized: Memory Pit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8757456897
    m_Localized: A disposal trench for bodies, drives, and erased records. Some entries
      keep answering.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8757456898
    m_Localized: Dead Transit Line
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8757456899
    m_Localized: An elevated rail corridor above the district. Fast routes, exposed
      fights.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8757456900
    m_Localized: Ruins Sector
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8757456901
    m_Localized: Collapsed megastructure blocks around the Last Kernel. Valuable
      systems are buried under hostile code.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651200
    m_Localized: Blueprint Packet
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651201
    m_Localized: A compressed build plan for district fabrication. Drag it into memory
      before the next blackout.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651202
    m_Localized: Dependent
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651203
    m_Localized: A district child under your protection. No output yet, but the future
      has weight.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651204
    m_Localized: Netrunner
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651205
    m_Localized: A field hacker who turns signal noise into weaponized breaches.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651206
    m_Localized: Scavenger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8761651207
    m_Localized: A sharp-eyed runner built for ranged work and salvage routes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845504
    m_Localized: Recruit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845505
    m_Localized: A district civilian pressed into service. Cheap, fragile, and necessary.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845506
    m_Localized: Enforcer
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845507
    m_Localized: A plated fighter for holding bad streets and breaking worse doors.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845508
    m_Localized: Volt Nut
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845509
    m_Localized: A small energy seed from a cracked hydro rack. Better toasted than
      raw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845510
    m_Localized: Synth Apple
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8765845511
    m_Localized: Clean fruit printed from old orchard templates. Small comfort, useful
      calories.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428416
    m_Localized: Heated Starch
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428417
    m_Localized: A hot block of dense carbohydrates. Not elegant, but it keeps workers
      upright.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428418
    m_Localized: Ration Pack
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428419
    m_Localized: Sealed calories from a supply cache. Basic fuel for another shift.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428420
    m_Localized: Coolant Pod
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428421
    m_Localized: A sealed fluid pod from flooded utility bays. Drinkable after filtering.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428422
    m_Localized: Protein Pod
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428423
    m_Localized: Lab-grown protein in a brittle membrane. Stable enough for cooking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428424
    m_Localized: Mixed Rations
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428425
    m_Localized: A compact meal assembled from clean produce. Efficient and easy
      to stack.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428426
    m_Localized: Nutrient Milk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428427
    m_Localized: Cultured feedstock with enough minerals to blunt hunger.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428428
    m_Localized: Med Gel
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428429
    m_Localized: A cold recovery slurry for shock, burns, and empty stomachs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8778428430
    m_Localized: Protein Fold
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8782622720
    m_Localized: Cooked protein with just enough texture to feel like food.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8782622721
    m_Localized: Starch Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8782622722
    m_Localized: A hardy hydroponic tuber grown in dirty nutrient trays.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8782622723
    m_Localized: Printed Protein
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8782622724
    m_Localized: Fresh tissue from a cheap vat printer. Cook before morale notices.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8791011328
    m_Localized: Toasted Volt Nut
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8791011329
    m_Localized: A toasted energy seed with a sharp chemical bite.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8795205632
    m_Localized: District Broth
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8795205633
    m_Localized: Hot water, protein scraps, and discipline. Enough to keep a crew
      moving.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8799399936
    m_Localized: Searpack
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8799399937
    m_Localized: Pressed protein flash-seared on a hot plate. Good morale per gram.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8799399938
    m_Localized: Reactor Stew
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8799399939
